task.summary:
reafactor: refactor DeleteImageFromOffer method in ProductImageService.cs to take IEnumerable of ProductImages as argument
This change skips unecessary DB calls - we already have product object while editing offer, so use it
refactor: refactor namespaces, views to use ViewBag, offer controller and service

refactor: make changes in all services to use new dtos
Created dtos for updation, addition and getting in services. Repaired unit tests. Changes not complete for OfferService.cs and co-existing components due to high complexity. Needed changes in mappings, and logical stuff
refactor: move files to corresponding folders
refactor: correct mappings, standarize dtos, repair views
refactor : cleanup services, refactor filtering to be done via ajax and partial views
feat: add possibility to filter user offers dynamically via ajax

refactor: change login view model to just LoginRequest.cs
Changed because there is no need for redundant class disguised as view model
refactor: delete PasswordChangeViewModel.cs instead use PasswordChangeRequest.cs
